SELECT ROUND(SUM(tiv_2016), 2) AS tiv_2016
FROM Insurance
WHERE tiv_2015 IN (
                  SELECT tiv_2015
                  FROM Insurance 
                  GROUP BY tiv_2015 
                  HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
                  )
      AND CONCAT(lat, lon) IN (
                              SELECT CONCAT(lat, lon)
                              FROM Insurance 
                              GROUP BY lat, lon 
                              HAVING COUNT(*) = 1
                              );
                              
Note:需要借鉴的东西在于where语句中。我觉得，这两个筛选条件很漂亮。
